title: ISic003372. I.Sicily inscription 003372
body:
Facsimile Images

1ΕΥΤΥΧΗΣΧΡΗΣΣ
2ΤΟΣΚΑΙΑΜ
3ΕΜΠΤΟΣΧΕΡ
4ΕΕΖΗΣΕΕΤΗΛ´

Apparatus criticus

Text after Manganaro 1962

English translation

Eutyches, worthy and blameless, farewell! He lived 30 years.>

commentary
